    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Seventeen letters written by Meredith Nicholson, 1896-1934 and n.d. 
Correspondents include William Gerard Chapman, Douglas Z. Doty, 
Richard Watson Gilder, Robert Underwood Johnson, Thomas L. Masson, 
William Henry Rideing, Charles Warren Stoddard, Will Orton Tewson, and 
Louis Joseph Vance.</p>
    </scopecontent>
